elf. You know not; perhaps Allah will bring about after that a [different] matter."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"فَإِذَا","d":"fa-idhā","e":"Then when","i":"فَاِذَا"},{"b":"0.69","h":"1.13","c":"بَلَغۡنَ","d":"balaghna","e":"they have reached","i":"بَلَغۡنَ"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.13","c":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","d":"ajalahunna","e":"their term","i":"اَجَلَهُنَّ"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.16","c":"فَأَمۡسِكُوهُنَّ","d":"fa-amsikūhunna","e":"then retain them","i":"فَاَمۡسِكُوۡهُنَّ"},{"b":"5.1","h":"7.22","c":"بِمَعۡرُوفٍ","d":"bimaʿrūfin","e":"with kindness","i":"بِمَعۡرُوۡفٍ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"9.18","c":"أَوۡ","d":"aw","e":"or","i":"اَوۡ"},{"b":"6.7","h":"9.7","c":"فَارِقُوهُنَّ","d":"fāriqūhunna","e":"part with them","i":"فَارِقُوۡهُنَّ"},{"b":"8.8","h":"12.56","c":"بِمَعۡرُوفٖ","d":"bimaʿrūfin","e":"with kindness","i":"بِمَعۡرُوۡفٍ"},{"b":"10.","h":"15.1","c":"وَأَشۡهِدُواْ","d":"wa-ashhidū","e":"And take witness","i":"وَّاَشۡهِدُوۡا"},{"b":"11.9","h":"16.71","c":"ذَوَيۡ","d":"dhaway","e":"two men","i":"ذَوَىۡ"},{"b":"12.4","h":"17.48","c":"عَدۡلٖ","d":"ʿadlin","e":"just","i":"عَدۡلٍ"},{"b":"13.8","h":"19.2","c":"مِّنكُمۡ","d":"minkum","e":"among you","i":"مِّنۡكُمۡ"},{"b":"15.2","h":"21.12","c":"وَأَقِيمُواْ","d":"wa-aqīmū","e":"and establish","i":"وَاَقِيۡمُوا"},{"b":"16.1","h":"22.61","c":"ٱلشَّهَٰدَةَ","d":"l-shahādata","e":"the testimony","i":"الشَّهَادَةَ"},{"b":"18","h":"24.48","c":"لِلَّهِۚ","d":"lillahi","e":"for Allah","i":"لِلّٰهِؕ"},{"b":"20.0","h":"29.65","c":"ذَٰلِكُمۡ","d":"dhālikum","e":"That","i":"ذٰ لِكُمۡ"},{"b":"21.0","h":"31.01","c":"يُوعَظُ","d":"yūʿaẓu","e":"is instructed","i":"يُوۡعَظُ"},{"b":"21.","h":"32.31","c":"بِهِۦ","d":"bihi","e":"with it","i":"بِهٖ"},{"b":"22.3","h":"33.21","c":"مَن","d":"man","e":"whoever","i":"مَنۡ"},{"b":"23.3","h":"34.27","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"[is]","i":"كَانَ"},{"b":"23.9","h":"35.18","c":"يُؤۡمِنُ","d":"yu'minu","e":"believes","i":"يُؤۡمِنُ"},{"b":"24.7","h":"36.27","c":"بِٱللَّهِ","d":"bil-lahi","e":"in Allah","i"