ُهٗؕ"},{"b":"9.1","h":"15.7","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"Indeed","i":"اِنَّ"},{"b":"10.4","h":"17.08","c":"ٱللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهَ"},{"b":"11.2","h":"18.42","c":"بَٰلِغُ","d":"bālighu","e":"(will) accomplish","i":"بَالِغُ"},{"b":"12.1","h":"19.63","c":"أَمۡرِهِۦۚ","d":"amrihi","e":"His purpose","i":"اَمۡرِهٖؕ"},{"b":"13.1","h":"22.1","c":"قَدۡ","d":"qad","e":"Indeed","i":"قَدۡ"},{"b":"13.4","h":"22.49","c":"جَعَلَ","d":"jaʿala","e":"has set","i":"جَعَلَ"},{"b":"14.0","h":"23.38","c":"ٱللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهُ"},{"b":"14.8","h":"24.77","c":"لِكُلِّ","d":"likulli","e":"for every","i":"لِكُلِّ"},{"b":"15.6","h":"25.93","c":"شَيۡءٖ","d":"shayin","e":"thing","i":"شَىۡءٍ"},{"b":"17.3","h":"27.93","c":"قَدۡرٗا","d":"qadran","e":"a measure","i":"قَدۡرًا"}],"a":{"g":"And will provide for him from where he does not expect. And whoever relies upon Allah - then He is sufficient for him. Indeed, Allah will accomplish His purpose. Allah has already set for everything a [decreed] extent."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"وَٱلَّـٰٓـِٔي","d":"wa-allāī","e":"And those who","i":"وَالّٰٓـىٴِۡ"},{"b":"2.4","h":"3.2","c":"يَئِسۡنَ","d":"ya-is'na","e":"have despaired","i":"يَٮِٕسۡنَ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.37","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"of","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.94","c":"ٱلۡمَحِيضِ","d":"l-maḥīḍi","e":"the menstruation","i":"الۡمَحِيۡضِ"},{"b":"4.5","h":"6.61","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"among","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"5.5","h":"7.69","c":"نِّسَآئِكُمۡ","d":"nisāikum","e":"your women","i":"نِّسَآٮِٕكُمۡ"},{"b":"7.9","h":"10.16","c":"إِنِ","d":"ini","e":"if","i":"اِنِ"},{"b":"8.3","h":"10.63","c":"ٱرۡتَبۡتُمۡ","d":"ir'tabtum","e":"you doubt","i":"ارۡتَبۡتُمۡ"},{"b":"9.3","h":"12.27","c":"فَعِدَّتُهُنَّ","d":"faʿiddatuhunna","e":"then their waiting period","i":"فَعِدَّتُهُنَّ"},{"b":"11.5","h":"15.12","c":"ثَلَٰثَةُ","d":"thalāthatu","e":"(is) three","i":"ثَلٰثَةُ"},{"b":"12.5","h":"16.86","c":"أَشۡهُرٖ","d":"ashhurin","e":"months","i":"اَشۡهُرٍ"},{"b":"13.","h":"18.88","c":"وَٱلَّـٰٓـِٔي","d":"wa-allāī","e":"and the ones who","i":"وَّالّٰٓـىٴِۡ"},{"b":"16.7","h":"21.84","c":"لَمۡ","d":"lam","e":"not","i":"لَمۡ"},{"b":"17.0","h":"22.37","c":"يَحِضۡنَۚ","d":"yaḥiḍ'na","e":"[they] menstruated","i":"يَحِضۡنَؕ"},{"b":"18.2","h":"27.66","c":"وَأُوْلَٰتُ","d":"wa-ulātu","e":"And those who (are)","i":"وَاُولَاتُ"},{"b":"19.2","h":"29.08","c":"ٱلۡأَحۡمَالِ","d":"l-aḥmāli","e":"pregnant","i":"الۡاَحۡمَالِ"},{"b":"20.3","h":"31.09","c":"أَجَلُهُنَّ","d":"ajaluhunna","e":"their term (is)","i":"اَجَلُهُنَّ"},{"b":"22.0","h":"33.42","c":"أَن","d":"an","e":"until","i":"اَنۡ"},{"b":"23.2","h":"34.56","c":"يَضَعۡنَ","d":"yaḍaʿna","e":"they deliver","i":"يَّضَعۡنَ"},{"b":"23.8","h":"35.72","c":"حَمۡلَهُنَّۚ","d":"ḥamlahunna","e":"their burdens","i":"حَمۡلَهُنَّؕ"},{"b":"25.9","h":"39.45","c":"وَمَن","d":"waman","e":"And whoever","i":"وَمَنۡ"},{"b":"27.2","h":"40.95","c":"يَتَّقِ","d":"yattaqi","e":"fears","i":"يَّـتَّـقِ"},{"b":"27.8","h":"42.15","c":"ٱللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهَ"},{"b":"28.6","h":"43.39","c":"يَجۡعَل","d":"yajʿal","e":"He will make","i":"يَجۡعَلْ"},{"b":"29.2","h":"44.74","c":"لَّهُۥ","d":"lahu","e":"for him","i":"لَّهٗ"},{"b":"30.0","h":"45.73","c":"مِنۡ","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"30.4","h":"46.32","c":"أَمۡرِهِۦ","d":"amrihi","e":"his affair","i":"اَمۡرِهٖ"},{"b":"31.","h":"48","c":"يُسۡرٗا","d":"yus'ran","e":"ease","i":"یُسْرًا"}],"a":{"g":"And those who no longer expect menstruation among your women - if you doubt, then their period is three months, and [also for] those who have not menstruated. And for those who are pregnant, their term is until they give birth. And whoever fears Allah - He will make for him of his matter ease."}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.35","c":"ذَٰلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"That","i":"ذٰ لِكَ"},{"b":"0.73","h":"1.53","c":"أَمۡرُ","d":"amru","e":"(is the) Command","i":"اَمۡرُ"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.55","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah","i":"الل